CHAPTER ______
1 AN ACT concerning
2 Health Facilities – Delegation of Inspection Authority – Nursing Homes
3 FOR the purpose of requiring the Secretary of Health, on request of a county, to delegate
4 to the county the authority to conduct site visits and full surveys and complaint
5 investigations of nursing homes; requiring the Maryland Department of Health to
6 execute a certain memorandum of understanding with a requesting county within a
7 certain period of time; requiring that the Maryland Department of Health and
8 certain counties equally share certain costs under certain circumstances; and
9 generally relating to the inspection of nursing homes and the delegation of authority.
10 BY repealing and reenacting, with amendments,
11 Article – Health – General
12 Section 19–1408
